<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    h1 {
      position: relative;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: slideFade 1.3s ease forwards;
    }

    @keyframes slideFade {
      0% {
        left: -40px;
        opacity: 0;
      }

      100% {
        left: 0;
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      #building {
        align-self: center;
        width: 250px;
        height: 250px;
      }
    }

    ;
  </style>
</head>

<%- include ('partials/header') %>

  <body>
    <div class="container text-light rounded-4" style="background-color: #000000;">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3 lh-base">
            Mastering <br> the Art of Saving
          </h1>
          <p class="lead col-lg-10">
            Saving isn't about how much you earn, it's about how much you keep. Take control of your money and not the
            other way around. With smart saving habits, even small amounts can grow into big wins over time.<br>
            Let's show you how to grow your savings, no matter your income.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-center">
          <img src="../static/images/savingshero.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-4 mt-3 mt-md-0"
            alt="Savings Hero Image" />
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="container py-3 mt-4 text-light" id="cards">
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4 mb-3" style="height: 100%">
          <div
            style="display:flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background: linear-gradient(to right, #7e0537 5%, #000000 100%); border-radius: 30px; min-height: 250px;">
            <div
              style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; height: 100%; text-align: center; justify-content: center;">
              <h2 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">70%</h2>
              <p style="margin: 0;">of Nigerians have no emergency savings.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4 mb-3">
          <div
            style="display:flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background: linear-gradient(to right, #85038a 5%, #000000 100%); border-radius: 30px; height: 250px;">

            <div
              style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; height:100%; align-items:  center; text-align: center; justify-content: center;">
              <h2 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">₦5000</h2>
              <p style="margin: 0;">saved monthly for 12 months = #60,000 + interest</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4 mb-3">
          <div
            style="display:flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background: linear-gradient(to right, #3d3d3d, #000000); border-radius: 30px; min-height: 250px;">

            <div
              style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; height:100%; align-items:  center; text-align: center; justify-content: center;">
              <h2 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">₦500/day</h2>
              <p style="margin: 0;">is all you need to build a 6-figure emergency fund in a year.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
      <div id="icon-grid">
        <h2 class="pb-2 display-6 fw-bold mt-5" style="text-align: center;">Popular Saving Strategies</h2>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-3 row-cols-lg-4 g-4 py-5">

          <div class="col">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.75em" height="1.75em" fill="currentColor"
                  class="bi bi-compass" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path
                    d="M8 16.016a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 1.962-14.74A1 1 0 0 0 9 0H7a1 1 0 0 0-.962 1.276A7.5 7.5 0 0 0 8 16.016m6.5-7.5a6.5 6.5 0 1 1-13 0 6.5 6.5 0 0 1 13 0" />
                  <path d="m6.94 7.44 4.95-2.83-2.83 4.95-4.949 2.83 2.828-4.95z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2 fs-5 text-light">50/30/20 Rule</h3>
                <p class="mb-0 text-light">
                  Save 20% of your income.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.75em" height="1.75em" fill="currentColor"
                  class="bi bi-slash-circle" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14m0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16" />
                  <path d="M11.354 4.646a.5.5 0 0 0-.708 0l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708l6-6a.5.5 0 0 0 0-.708" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2 fs-5 text-light">Envelope Method</h3>
                <p class="mb-0 text-light">
                  Allocate cash into spending categories.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.75em" height="1.75em" fill="currentColor"
                  class="bi bi-piggy-bank" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path
                    d="M5 6.25a.75.75 0 1 1-1.5 0 .75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0m1.138-1.496A6.6 6.6 0 0 1 7.964 4.5c.666 0 1.303.097 1.893.273a.5.5 0 0 0 .286-.958A7.6 7.6 0 0 0 7.964 3.5c-.734 0-1.441.103-2.102.292a.5.5 0 1 0 .276.962" />
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M7.964 1.527c-2.977 0-5.571 1.704-6.32 4.125h-.55A1 1 0 0 0 .11 6.824l.254 1.46a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.478 1.243h.263c.3.513.688.978 1.145 1.382l-.729 2.477a.5.5 0 0 0 .48.641h2a.5.5 0 0 0 .471-.332l.482-1.351c.635.173 1.31.267 2.011.267.707 0 1.388-.095 2.028-.272l.543 1.372a.5.5 0 0 0 .465.316h2a.5.5 0 0 0 .478-.645l-.761-2.506C13.81 9.895 14.5 8.559 14.5 7.069q0-.218-.02-.431c.261-.11.508-.266.705-.444.315.306.815.306.815-.417 0 .223-.5.223-.461-.026a1 1 0 0 0 .09-.255.7.7 0 0 0-.202-.645.58.58 0 0 0-.707-.098.74.74 0 0 0-.375.562c-.024.243.082.48.32.654a2 2 0 0 1-.259.153c-.534-2.664-3.284-4.595-6.442-4.595Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2 fs-5 text-light">Pay Yourself First</h3>
                <p class="mb-0 text-light">
                  Automate saving before spending.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.75em" height="1.75em" fill="currentColor"
                  class="bi bi-list-check" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M5 11.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h9a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-9a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5m0-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h9a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-9a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5m0-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h9a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-9a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5M3.854 2.146a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-.5-.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L2 3.293l1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0m0 4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-.5-.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L2 7.293l1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0m0 4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-.5-.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708l.146.147 1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2 fs-5 text-light">Zero-Based Budgeting</h3>
                <p class="mb-0 text-light">
                  Account for every naira
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <section class="container py-4 text-light mb-3">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mt-3">
            <h2 class="mb-3 fw-bold display-6">Building the Habit</h2>
            <ul class="ps-3">
              <li>Set a savings goal (e.g., ₦100,000 in 6 months)</li>
              <li>Open a separate account just for savings</li>
              <li>Automate your deposits every payday</li>
              <li>Use budgeting apps to track your spending</li>
              <li>Cut non-essentials and redirect funds to savings</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
            <img id="building" src="../static/images/buildingsavings.webp" height="225" width="450"
              style="border-radius: 20px; margin: 20px;" />
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </section>

    <section id="savings-calculator" class="py-5 polka-bg text-white">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-4 reveal-up">
          <h2 class="fw-bold">Savings Calculator</h2>
          <p class="mb-0">Calculate your savings according to your goals and interest.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
          <!-- LEFT: Form -->
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 reveal-up">
            <div class="card glass-card p-4">
              <!-- Currency toggle -->
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <small class="text-success">Choose currency :</small>
                <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="currency switch">
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light currency-btn" data-symbol="₦"
                    data-currency="USD">NGN</button>
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light active currency-btn" data-symbol="$"
                    data-currency="USD">USD</button>
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light currency-btn" data-symbol="€"
                    data-currency="EUR">EUR</button>
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light currency-btn" data-symbol="£"
                    data-currency="GBP">GBP</button>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Inputs -->
              <form id="calcForm" class="row g-3">
                <div class="col-12">
                  <label class="form-label visually-hidden" for="starting">Starting Balance</label>
                  <input type="text" step="0.01" min="0" id="starting" class="form-control form-control-dark"
                    placeholder="Starting Balance (e.g. 1,000)" />
                </div>

                <div class="col-12">
                  <label class="form-label visually-hidden" for="monthly">Monthly Contribution</label>
                  <input type="text" step="0.01" min="0" id="monthly" class="form-control form-control-dark"
                    placeholder="Monthly Contribution (e.g. 200)" />
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <label class="form-label visually-hidden" for="period">Period</label>
                  <input type="number" min="0" id="period" class="form-control form-control-dark"
                    placeholder="Period (number)" />
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <label class="form-label visually-hidden" for="periodUnit">Unit</label>
                  <select id="periodUnit" class="form-select form-select-dark">
                    <option value="months">Months</option>
                    <option value="years" selected>Years</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="col-12">
                  <label class="form-label visually-hidden" for="rate">Annual interest rate (%)</label>
                  <input type="number" step="0.01" min="0" id="rate" class="form-control form-control-dark"
                    placeholder="Annual interest rate (%) e.g. 12" />
                </div>

                <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-start mt-3">
                  <button id="calculateBtn" type="button"
                    class="btn btn-success btn-lg rounded-pill px-4 text-light">Calculate</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card glass-card result-card p-5 text-center reveal-up">
              <div class="mb-3 text-success">Your balance saving position</div>
              <div class="display-6 fw-bold result-amount" aria-live="polite">$0.00</div>

              <div class="row mt-4 gx-3">
                <div class="col-6">
                  <div class="small text-success">Total Contributed</div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold small contrib-amount">$0.00</div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                  <div class="small text-success">Total Interest Earned</div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold small interest-amount">$0.00</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-4 text-white fst-italic fw-light small ">
                Results assume monthly compounding and contributions at month end.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-center text-light py-5 mt-5"
      style="background: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(28, 28, 28), black)">
      <h2 class="fw-bold">Start Saving Today</h2>
      <p class="lead">Small amounts over time lead to big results. Start now and thank yourself later.</p>
      <a href="/budget" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg mt-3 rounded-5">Create a Target</a>
    </section>

  </body>
  <%- include ('partials/footer') %>